al feature.\n\n**Evaluating Spring Boot Annotations**\n\nI'm considering whether the ApplicationContextRunner can provide an @AutoConfigurationPackage class within a package. It seems that this annotation registers only the packages of annotated classes. To choose a dependency package, I might need to use @AutoConfigurationPackage with basePackages. I should look into Spring Boot 2.5 to see if this annotation offers basePackages. Maybe I can check its implementation, possibly by using javap, since it likely does based on Spring Boot 2.3.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_02a81ebd13c1d321016a2530970e8881909a94ef22f7b74aef\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJTCo247gWkXuhxLK-cCJrwFJzsYU6Ui519kQryg7Cr_qVtcJ2BLAWkQsq80XQp5NbzMFRmxA1ZsPobiU0IJHM3pQEa0md1ltMMAoajytX5njpXDc_svVySLxkHWrkA_veqYu47EvzUrnKj6a5sIWZjGcoMFQYUHfAKILPZ1POW7pfCyyS_WCyVFxTkFVH87JBp6sTDqDnki_1aKIOvQInUbrco3d3UVWqEpEiQOgZszoX0AdWDpOAA3PVFx_DDoiFAlJJVPlCwDC2kKzblU7poRzp4cMPPYUnLgVu6TMEpfD-e-hekCepUfOMzW0j6MdVusWDbDAtgLeH9YgWMiMcwCQqtFYitucXFrIbbNyf766TKiePVLm9OSnMgrP7ETITMefMvoEDygl5UJHbXTRq8ahPJ05YrR11Co0ECGjmVZh5S2P6itM2yfEKgPzfLTwGFBjawsJidlj2tQMlLVYh7oUrJsk9v30mxSM5LiPKRLmVESYdg5dJTRdFU57HRjMenP3oHtrHQ1ojWPz512lYVx-TrbfDtW6sPLgr18NH9-KvUYJNSMoBge9fa1PUvhx2X-G37TYb0JfKmzO4MHwCdCiuDbGRDY3mKfbZw6zRNXETVvSWijPY_6VP1FWstXIpXZZdvTGT7P0VDx6vpXgp-vNKFuD5DTR8sj7WnDZFH8bZ0IQnaaYdA3Chd36rXyAYFJcq3XcKcd7VnPcfGuzs-47z2vzprma0bdjGRz-t4iy6FaXZxBimN8JQmsEhkq7qrXjXBFG66RRmInyKX551n8-WN2FrF1ihwBZLyy3AVBtrejJgydi6RyQAk8rPk5hnkGvTflUHDUge78o5xSqbFjDyYubEDxN5y5kx8Fkr_FgV_6T6QGRrUJkvAeC3NjtxybKsi2beqdJZKyupBHmA6G-QngBAeymfQGdGeDzvx_BVgWsQXEkM1fdomHhq9equ8cqIsvx4Ft0l7hH9pz43RKBu6CJgqkO7omiG1WmF0UN_xROocK2b73-9Xl3czeUn56uPH8Cetvar5pfgYnZh4Odx3x4ZR4jbdIn3jlOTVC2kBp1sa0Q4GSzh_-EWlb9tnPodlGiiE-5oO_tanV7parU1wjvLgGh8RVu0tDBuK63XUrgP4xa18nZIGSw-3Qr7Sps9J8fc7urEUwcxe8vs0hx898a4sdupMeN_T26z08f6N_5NWBaHC1BWXwNv4hAPUlYQ2bYoxRdJLLBySrqYKaG1cS5RIpEuoC7Sv4li-er0ACEEr13Qg_XhQxZafYBG1MqHqPRvFwpp-in